import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom';

function Content() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <PhoneticsList/>
      </Route>
      <Route exact path="/examples/:name">
        <ExampleOfPhonetic/>
      </Route>
    </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>  
  )
}
export default  Content
